\mt1 Fas Tesalonaeka  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip Pol ramav…ôn mam…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo ia kwopun me. Ia nav…ônien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ro k…ôru ir…ô r…ôrpwi vi a nous…ôs…®mw…®nien s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me fwe Tesalonaeka. In rar…ô fwe ik…®n n…ôfwakiien kahar n…ôn…ô mier t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôkur Isrel h…ômw…ôki in, mhomet…ô in. Ia nuk 51 Timoti r…ôrhi pen n…ôkuku…ô riti rev…ôn t…® Pol mam…ô…°kiari ia nar…ôien s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me fwe Tesalonaeka. Pol ramar…ô fwe Korin n…ôp…®n in ruvehi n…ôkuku…ô s…ôv…ôi Timoti. In rokeikei m…ô truvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Tesalonaeka ro pen r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i. Pol r…®nam…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni n…ôkur Tesalonaeka t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ham…ôr…ôr …ôknek…®n ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha n…ôp…®n n…ôrmama hamomet…ô ir…ôha. In ramahat…ôn ir…ôha ia nar…ôien s…ô ratukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, mamahat…ôn mwi ir…ôha ia nuveheien s…ôv…ôi Iesu. K…®taha s…ôreirei m…ô Iesu truvehe ia n…ôfe n…ôp…®n. Ro pen tsam…ômwur ia noien amasan meste nuveheien s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Wok Me 17:1-10, 2Tes 1:1\x*Iou Pol, Saelas, m…®ne Timoti.  
\p N…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha nakalasia me fwe Tesalonaeka. K…®miaha n…ôrmama s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn tata s…ôk…®taha m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.  
\p Pw…ôh namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien krauar…ô tukumiaha.   
\s1 K…®ni vivi Kumwes…ôn t…® nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Tesalonaeka  
\p
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Fil 1:3-4, Kol 1:3, 2Tes 1:11\x*N…ôp…®n me pam iaham…ôni k…®miaha ia n…ôfwakiien me s…ôk…®maha, n…ôn…ô mamh…ôni vivi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha pam,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1Kor 13:13, Kol 1:4-6\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha rer…®maha ramrhi noien amasan s…ôk…®miaha s…ô ruku pen ia nahat…ôt…ôien, m…®ne n…ômwurien s…ôk…®miaha s…ô ruku pen ia nokeikeiien, m…®ne n…ôrerien s…ôk…®miaha s…ô hiam…ôrer …ôknek…®n ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hi…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ia I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo.   
\p
\v 4 Piak me, Kumwes…ôn rokeikei k…®miaha, n…ôn…ô muv…ôrfi raka k…®miaha m…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi. K…®maha iah…ôukur…ôn amasan m…ô n…ôri n…ôha ro n…®p…ôrhienien  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 1Kor 2:4-5, 1Kor 4:20\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô iaham…ôvisau irapw i r…®m…ôuvehe tukumiaha fwe kupw…ôn, r…®pkuvehe mh…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien a, m…ôt…ô ruvehe mwi ia n…ô…°sen, m…®ne N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan, m…®ne ia suatuk riti s…ô rahat…ôn pen m…ô hiamahat…ôt…ô p…ôrhien ir…ô. N…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n iah…ônar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha, hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô iah…ôn…ôfar…ô ir…ô. Iah…ôno a narimnari me rasitu ia k…®miaha.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1Kor 4:16, 2Tes 3:9, Wok Me 17:5-9\x*N…ôn…ô ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha hi…ôuvehe mh…ômwhen a ia k…®maha m…®ne I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n kuvei pehe n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn m k…®miaha n…ôn…ô hi…ôuvehi n…ôrmama ho n…ômis…ôien asori m k…®miaha, m…ôt…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan ro rer…®miaha ra…°ien a.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1Tes 5:3\x*Ia noien n…ôha hi…ônahat…ôn suatuk amasan riti m n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamhahat…ôt…ô fwe profens mi n…ôha Masetonia m…®ne Akaea m…ô tuhesi pen noien s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Rom 1:8\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®miaha hi…ôn…ôvisau irapw raka n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu kuv…ôre…°i ia kwopun me r…ômwhen ia kis…®pw ras…ôk. R…®pko mh…ô fwe Masetonia …ôpa m…®ne Akaea, m…ôt…ô n…ôrmama ia kwopun me pam h…ôuv…ôre…°i raka kam…®ni m…ô hi…ôn…ôfo mh…ôuvehe mhahat…ôt…ô ia Kumwes…ôn. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô k…®maha tah…ôni n…ô…°kiariien riti t…® n…ôfe.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Wok Me 14:15\x*N…ôrmama me pam n…ôha kamh…ô…°kiari ia k…®taha, mamh…ôni m…ô n…ôp…®n iah…ôuvehe mh…ôt…ô k…®miaha fwe kupw…ôn, hi…ôsev…ôr ia rer…®miaha tukumaha, n…ôn…ô mharaka ia n…ôn…®mwi nari me s…ôk…®miaha s…ôm…ôme hiam…ôfwaki pen m…®nraha, mh…ôuvehe mh…ôkurir…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ôk…®maha. Ir…ôha kamh…ôni m…ô ipwet m…®ne hiamo tukwini nari m Kumwes…ôn p…ôrhien s…ô ram…®ru,  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Taet 2:13, Wok Me 17:31, 1Tes 5:9\x*mamheitenhi t…®ni s…ô in r…®no r…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien. T…®ni n…ôha Iesu s…ô truku pen ia neiai, muvehe, muvehi raka k…®taha t…® niemaha s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ia n…ôp…®n rauvehe.   
\c 2  
\s1 Wok s…ô Pol r…®no fwe Tesalonaeka  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1Tes 1:5,9\x*Piak me, k…®miaha hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ôp…®n iah…ôuvehe mh…ôtoni k…®miaha fwe kupw…ôn, nuveheien s…ôk…®maha r…®pko mh…ô n…ôri au…ôr a ir…ô.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Wok Me 16:19-24, Wok Me 17:1-9\x*Hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ôp…®n iahamar…ô ihi fwe Filipae, n…ôrmama ho n…ômis…ôien m k…®maha, mh…ôni …ôr…ôha k…®maha. M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ôk…®taha r…®no n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®maha r…®skai iah…ôuvehe mh…ôni irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi tukumiaha ia n…ômri n…ôrmama h…ôp…®k s…ôm…ôme h…ômw…ôki n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha.  
\v 3 N…ôn…ô hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôk…®maha iah…ôn…ôvisau irapw m k…®miaha rier ia t…ôrhumaha t…® n…ôfe? T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iah…ôrkwaf…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien …ôr…ôha riti ia rer…®maha, u…ô iah…ômwur m…ô taheiku…ô ia k…®miaha, u…ô taho n…®feifeiien m k…®miaha? Rek…ôm!  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt 1Tim 1:11, Kal 1:10, Jer 11:20\x*Iah…ôpw…ôh noien iam…®nha ir…ô, m…ôt…ô ia n…ôp…®n me iaham…ôni n…ô…°kiariien s…ô Kumwes…ôn rokeikei, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in r…®n…ôt…ô raka k…®maha m…ô iah…ômwhen, r…ômri pehe n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi ia t…®pa…°e r…ô…°…®maha. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô iah…ôpk…ômwur mh…ô m…ô n…ôrmama rer…®nraha tra…°ien tukumaha, m…ôt…ô iaham…ômwur m…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ô ram…ôt…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®maha rer…®n tra…°ien tukumaha.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Wok Me 20:33, 2Tes 2:3, Rom 1:9, 1Tes 2:10\x*R…ômwhen k…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka k…®maha iah…ôpkuvehe mh…ô mh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien …ôsien me tukumiaha, u…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ô tah…ôvi k…®miaha ir…ô hi…ôuvehe mh…ôuvei pehe mane m k…®maha. Kumwes…ôn mwi rukur…ôn m…ô n…ô…°kiariien i ro n…®p…ôrhienien!  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jon 5:41,44\x*N…ôn…ô iah…ôpk…ômwur mh…ô m…ô taho n…ôrmama h…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni k…®maha. Iah…ôpw…ôh noien iam…®nhi ir…ô ia k…®miaha u…ô ia n…ôrmama nepw…®n mwi.   
\p
\v 7 N…ôn…ô nari riti t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®maha aposol me s…ôv…ôi Kristo iah…ôukur…ôn n…®niien m…ô tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôsiai k…®maha r…ômwhen ia n…ôm…ô asori me, m…ôt…ô iah…ôpko mh…ô iam…®nhi ir…ô. N…ôp…®n iahamar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha fwe kupw…ôn, noien s…ôk…®maha r…®m…ôru r…ômwhen ia mama riti s…ô ram…ôtui amasan t…® n…®pwn…ôt…®n me.  
\v 8 Iahokeikei p…®k k…®miaha, ro pen ia n…ôp…®n me n…ôha rer…®maha ra…°ien t…® n…®ni irapwien n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha. M…ôt…ô r…®pko mh…ô in …ôpa i, rer…®maha ra…°ien a mwi t…® nuvei peheien n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha m k…®miaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iahokeikei p…®k k…®miaha.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Wok Me 20:34, 1Kor 4:12\x*Piak me, rer…®miaha ramrhi wok skai s…ô iah…ôno u…ô rek…ôm? N…ôp…®n iaham…ôni irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha, iahamo wok ia r…ô…°…®maha ia n…ôp…®n m…®ne ia ran m…ô tah…ôpw…ôh n…ôres peheien nari riti tukumiaha.   
\p
\v 10 K…®miaha m…®ne Kumwes…ôn mwi hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ô…°kiariien i ro n…®p…ôrhienien! N…ôp…®n iahamar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha n…ôrmama hiamahat…ôt…ô ia Kumwes…ôn, noien s…ôk…®maha ro ikinan, matukwatukw, m…ômher.  
\v 11 Hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô iah…ôno m k…®miaha r…ômwhen ia tata riti ramo m n…®pwn…ôt…®n me.  
\v 12 Iaham…ôrpwi …ôknek…®n k…®miaha, mamh…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha, n…ôn…ô mamh…ô…°kiari skai m k…®miaha m…ô tihar…ô ia nar…ôien s…ô ratukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn. In ram…ôkwein k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôuvehe ia n…ôkwai n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô in ram…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô mamh…ôhiapw.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt 1Tes 1:2, 2Tes 2:13, Kal 1:11-12\x*Nari riti mwi n…ôha ik…®n ia n…ôp…®n me pam iaham…ôni vivi Kumwes…ôn tukwe. N…ôp…®n iah…ôni pehe n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha, k…®miaha hi…ôre…°i, mh…ôuvehi n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha, mh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô. Hi…ôpkuvehi mh…ô n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha r…ômwhen ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama, m…ôt…ô hi…ôuvehi atukwatukw mh…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ô…°kiariien i in p…ôrhien n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn. N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha rauver…ô ia k…®miaha s…ôm…ôme hiam…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Wok Me 17:5\x*Piak me, hi…ôukur…ôn nakalasia me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn fwe t…ôn…ô Jutia kamh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Iesu Kristo. K…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôuvehe mh…ôn…ômwhen raka ia nir…ôha. Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ômis…ôien me n…ôha n…ôkur Isrel h…ôno m…®nraha n…ôkur imw…ômiaha me h…ôno r…ômwhen a mwi ia k…®miaha.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Wok Me 2:23, 7:52\x*N…ôkur Isrel me n…ôha ir…ôha h…ônousi …ôpune Iesu I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha, m…®ne profet kupw…ôn me, n…ôn…ô mh…ôkoui irapw k…®maha iah…ôier. Kumwes…ôn rer…®n r…®pka…°ien anan mh…ô t…® nir…ôha. Ir…ôha kamh…ômw…ôki n…ôrmama me pam,  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Mat 23:32-33\x*mamh…ômwur m…ô tuh…ônise k…®maha iah…ôpw…ôh n…ô…°kiariien m n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel kamo Kumwes…ôn ruvehim…®ru ir…ôha. Ia noien n…ôha kamhakutan pen noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônraha meste truku…ôr. M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni n…ôha niemaha s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôuvehe m…®neste ir…ôha.   
\s1 Pol rokeikei p…®k m…ô tr…ôtoni mwi n…ôkur Tesalonaeka  
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1Tes 3:10\x*Piak me, fwe kupw…ôn k…®maha iah…ôn…ôpw…ôh k…®miaha ia n…®pwramaha mh…ôuv…ôn isipw…®n tukumiaha s…ôv…ôi n…ôp…®n ouihi, m…ôt…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®maha ram…ômak ihi ia k…®miaha. Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha iaham…ômwur p…®k m…ô tah…ôr…ôr…®…° mh…ôtoni mwi k…®miaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iahokeikei p…®k k…®miaha.  
\v 18 Iah…ônokeikei m…ô tah…ôuvehe mh…ôtoni k…®miaha, iou, Pol, iakani p…ôrhien m…ô iak…®n…ômwur n…ôp…®n r…®p…®k, m…ôt…ô Setan r…ôsis…ô…° k…®maha.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Fil 2:15-16, 4:1, 2Tes 1:4\x*N…ôfe n…ôha iaham…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®maha ir…ô, u…ô n…ôfe n…ôha na…°ienien s…ôk…®maha m…®ne k…ôf…ôfau s…ôv…ôi n…®siaiien s…ô tah…ôrpwi k…®maha tukwe ia n…ômri I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu n…ôp…®n in truvehe ir…ô? Rosi k…®miaha n…ô u…ô?  
\v 20 Ou…ôh n…®p…ôrhienien, k…®miaha n…ô n…ôrmama iaham…ôrpwi k…®maha tukumiaha, n…ôn…ô rer…®maha rama…°ien tukumiaha.   
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Wok Me 17:15\x*N…ôp…®n k…®maha iah…ôuvav…ôn isipw…®n tukumiaha, rer…®maha r…ôpou p…®k t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iah…ôreirei m…ô hiamar…ô amasan u…ô rek…ôm. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô iah…ôni s…®mw…®n m…ô iou m…®ne Saelas trauar…ô k…®mrau …ôpa ia taon n…ôha Atens,  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Wok Me 16:1-3\x*m…ôt…ô Timoti truvehe m…ôtoni k…®miaha. In pi…ôvtaha riti s…ô ramo wok s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn k…®maha min, iaham…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo. K…®maha iah…ôrhi pehe in tukumiaha m…ô trasitu ia k…®miaha muvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha, n…ôn…ô m…ôrpwi …ôknek…®n k…®miaha ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Efes 3:13, 2Tim 3:12\x*m…ô n…ômis…ôien me i kamo m k…®miaha tuh…ôpw…ôh noien k…®miaha riti r…®mwei. Hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka m…ô n…ôri in i k…®m…ôrfi raka m…ô tuko m k…®taha iam…®nhi ir…ô.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Wok Me 14:22\x*N…ôp…®n iahamar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha fwe kupw…ôn iaham…ôni pehe tukumiaha m…ô tuko n…ômis…ôien m k…®taha. N…ôn…ô hi…ôukur…ôn amasan m…ô ruv…ôuvehe m…®no n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô r…ômwhen iah…ôm…ôni tukumiaha i.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Fil 2:16\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôp…®n rer…®k r…ôpou p…®k t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakreirei m…ô hiamar…ô amasan u…ô rek…ôm n…ôn…ô iak…ôrhi pehe Timoti m…ô truvehe m…ôtoni ro nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha m…ô ramskai ihi u…ô rek…ôm. Iakamhek…®r m…ô ia suatuk riti Setan s…ô ram…ômwur m…ô tro n…ôrmama h…ômwei ia n…ôr…ôhaien r…®no raka k…®miaha hi…ômwei ia n…ôr…ôhaien, n…ôn…ô wok s…ôk…®maha tro n…ôri au…ôr a ir…ô.   
\s1 Timoti r…®r…ôr…®…° pehe m…ôvisau n…ô…°kiariien amasan riti m Pol m…®ne Saelas  
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Wok Me 18:5\x*T…ôkwt…ôkwuni n…ôha Timoti ruv…ôr…ôr…®…° pehe mwi tukumaha, n…ôn…ô m…ôvisau pehe m k…®maha n…ô…°kiariien amasan i ram…ô…°kiari ia nahat…ôt…ôien m…®ne nokeikeiien s…ôk…®miaha. In r…®m…ôni pehe tukumaha i m…ô rer…®miaha ramrhi ihi k…®maha ia na…°ienien, n…ôn…ô mhokeikei m…ô tih…ôtoni k…®maha r…ômwhen a ia k…®maha iahokeikei m…ô tah…ôtoni k…®miaha.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 2Tes 1:4\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô, piak me, n…ôri au…ôr a iahamre…°i r…ôr…ôha ia n…ômis…ôien me i kamo m k…®maha, m…ôt…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha r…®m…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®maha tukumiaha.  
\v 8 N…ôp…®n k…®maha iah…ôre…°i m…ô k…®miaha hiam…ôrer …ôknek…®n t…® I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha iah…ôre…°i m…ô iah…ôuvehi mwi n…®m…®ruien.  
\v 9 Ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn s…ôk…®taha rer…®maha rama…°ien tukumiaha. Na…°ienien n…ôha rasori p…®k mamo k…®maha iaham…ôni vivi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha.  
\v 10 Ia n…ôp…®n me pam ia n…ôp…®n m…®ne ia ran iaham…ôfwaki skai m…ô tah…ôtoni mwi k…®miaha, mhahat…ôn k…®miaha ia n…ôfe hi…ôreirei ihi m…ô nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha tr…®skai mwi.   
\p
